Description:                               =
============================================

Paranormal State: Poison Spring is a fast-paced and terrifying Hidden Object Light Adventure game from Legacy Games. In Paranormal State: Poison Spring, you get to join the ace team from A&amp;E's hit show Paranormal State and help people who are being terrorized from something not of this world. Poison Spring State Park was the site of a bloody Civil War battle in 1864... but something is still fighting there today. Only you can solve the mystery of what has happened here, and lay any restless spirits to rest. Solve perplexing puzzles and search for cleverly hidden clues to save the park before it's too late!

